When I was a kid I spent summers in the country. My father stayed in the city and sent me letters. There was no internet at the time. Once he sent me an unusual ciphered letter. It could not be read without a cardboard key which he attached as well. I was so happy, the thing looked magical. Today I want to share this magic. Generate a key and create a letter for someone close to you. You can print and send it with share button. Sometimes it is not easy to find the right words. And maybe easier to share something personal and ciphered. Dedicated to my dad who I love and miss being far abroad.